\c 25
\s Rwiyo rwekurumbidza Jehovha
\p
\v 1 Jehovha, muri Mwari wangu! Ndichakusimudzirai, ndirumbidze zita renyu, nokuti makaita chinoshamisa; mazano ekare ane kutendeka \add uye\add* chokwadi.
\v 2 Nokuti makaita guta rive churu, guta rakashoshewa rive dongo; nzvimbo yakakwirira yevatorwa isava guta; haringavakwi kusvika rinhi narinhi.
\v 3 Naizvozvo vanhu vane simba vachakurumbidzai; guta remarudzi anotyisa richakutyai.
\v 4 Nokuti manga muri simba kumurombo, simba kune anoshaiwa pakutambudzika kwake, uvando kubva kudutu remhepo ine mvura, mumvuri pakupisa, kana mhepo yevanotyisa ichiita sedutu remhepo ine mvura parusvingo.
\v 5 Muchaderedza ruzha rwevatorwa sekupisa panzvimbo yakaoma; \add sezvinoitwa\add* kupisa nemumvuri wegore, rwiyo rwevane utsinye rwuchaderedzwa.
\p
\v 6 Zvino pagomo iri Jehovha wehondo achaitira vanhu vose mabiko ezvinhu zvakakora, mabiko ewaini zhinji pamasese, ezvinhu zvakakora zvizere nemongo, wewaini zhinji pamasese yakasvinwa zvakanaka.
\v 7 Zvino achamedza pagomo iri chiso chebutiro rakaputira vanhu vese, nechifukidzo chakawaridzwa pamusoro pemarudzi ose.
\v 8 Wakamedza rufu mukukunda; uye Ishe Jehovha achapusika misodzi kubva pazviso zvose; nekushoorwa kwevanhu vake achabvisa pasi pose; nokuti Jehovha wataura.
\p
\v 9 Zvino nezuva iro kuchanzi: Tarirai, uyu ndiye Mwari wedu; takamumirira, uye achatiponesa; uyu ndiJehovha; takamumirira; tichafara nekupembera muruponeso rwake.
\v 10 Nokuti ruoko rwaJehovha ruchazorora pagomo iri; naMoabhu vachatsikirwa pasi pake, semajanga akaunganidzwa anotsikirwa mugomba remupfudze.
\v 11 Zvino achatandavadzira maoko ake pakati paro, sekutandavadza kunoita mushambiri kuti ashambire; uye achaderedza kuzvikudza kwaro pamwe chete nekuvandira kwemaoko aro.
\v 12 Zvino nhare yakakwirira yemasvingo enyu achaiputsira pasi, aideredze pasi, aisvitse muvhu muguruva.